ore":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T08:56:32.000Z","msg":"我先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1.去兆萬間青葉。唔好食都係其次，份量真係吹脹。<br />\n魚生細細件食刀功，叫個牛肉鍋食諗住細細鍋好似吉野家咁試下啦，點知黎左個FULL SIZE既不銹鋼鍋連埋個FULL SIZE既爐頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.第一次接觸放題係登打士街間2000円，心諗嘩百零蚊有甜蝦任食好抵呀。十年後諗起都<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T14:28:55.000Z","msg":"有間hihi 放題同一座，叫乜都漏單，得炸Mac 樂雞，呃人錢"},{"pid":"2503a0203476f5c780ef4ab40203f9a082c18f95","tid":2489932,"uid":43731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T14:31:10.000Z","msg":"兆萬d放題真係狗也不屌"},{"pid":"eb85dff14f53acfb3f583500585374373af7eda4","tid":2489932,"uid":54930,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T14:35:16.000Z","msg":"25歲，仲係會想食放題<br />\n不過已經冇朋友一齊食<br />\n計返都有3，4年冇食過<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fca3cb2c4ced9e1e1f7758ebb7f764d91d1bff44","tid":2489932,"uid":4850,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T14:37:44.000Z","msg":"兆萬勇者塔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f79e6f444d447419751b1e866c1174665154e82","tid":2489932,"uid":149122,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T15:06:54.000Z","msg":"嗰陣都會一班人一齊食放題 韓燒<br />\n十年後莫講話放題<br />\n肉都食少咗<br />\n重點係班人都一樣好耐唔見"},{"pid":"746e38d95701c0e13834830eced7ac0f284b27b6","tid":2489932,"uid":41803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62dbf3b6bf2e39077d72fdd33f9dc1dc90295a84","tid":2489932,"uid":41803,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T13:55:24.000Z","msg":"究竟有無黃店做漢燒或者放題？